 You if are reading this message something went wrong.
 Make sure to run the Docker container with at least the following options

 # docker run --privileged --mount type=volume,source=fun4all,target=/app preghenella/fun4all

 I suggest you add a few more options and bind the current directory

 # docker run --privileged --rm -it --mount type=volume,source=fun4all,target=/app --mount type=bind,source=`pwd`,target=/home/docker preghenella/fun4all

